<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>Emotional Vault: Setoran vs Tarikan</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rajdhani:wght@400;600;700&family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap');

        :root {
            --neon-green: #39ff14;
            --neon-red: #ff073a;
            --cyber-blue: #0ff;
            --dark-bg: #0d1117;
            --panel-bg: #161b22;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--dark-bg);
            color: #c9d1d9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(rgba(13, 17, 23, 0.9), rgba(13, 17, 23, 0.9)),
                repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #161b22 0px, #161b22 2px, transparent 2px, transparent 10px);
        }

        .font-mono { font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace; }

        /* Cyber-Industrial UI Elements */
        .cyber-panel {
            background-color: var(--panel-bg);
            border: 1px solid #30363d;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.1), inset 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            border-radius: 8px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .cyber-panel::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -1px; left: -1px;
            width: 20px; height: 20px;
            border-top: 2px solid var(--cyber-blue);
            border-left: 2px solid var(--cyber-blue);
            border-radius: 8px 0 0 0;
        }

        .neon-text-blue { text-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--cyber-blue); color: var(--cyber-blue); }
        .neon-text-green { text-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--neon-green); color: var(--neon-green); }
        .neon-text-red { text-shadow: 0 0 5px var(--neon-red); color: var(--neon-red); }

        .btn-cyber {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.2), transparent);
            border: 1px solid var(--cyber-blue);
            color: var(--cyber-blue);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
        .btn-cyber:hover {
            background-color: var(--cyber-blue);
            color: var(--dark-bg);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--cyber-blue);
        }
        .btn-cyber:disabled {
            border-color: #555; color: #555; background: none; box-shadow: none; cursor: not-allowed;
        }

        /* Drag & Drop Areas */
        .drop-zone {
            transition: all 0.3s;
            border: 2px dashed #555;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .drop-zone.green { border-color: rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.5); }
        .drop-zone.red { border-color: rgba(255, 7, 58, 0.5); }
        
        .drop-zone.green.active-drag { border-color: var(--neon-green); background: rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.1); box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--neon-green); }
        .drop-zone.red.active-drag { border-color: var(--neon-red); background: rgba(255, 7, 58, 0.1); box-shadow: 0 0 15px var(--neon-red); }

        .draggable-card {
            background: #21262d;
            border: 1px solid var(--cyber-blue);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            cursor: grab;
            touch-action: none; /* Prevent scrolling while dragging */
            z-index: 50;
            user-select: none;
        }
        .draggable-card:active { cursor: grabbing; }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes shake {
            0% { transform: translate(1px, 1px) rotate(0deg); }
            10% { transform: translate(-1px, -2px) rotate(-1deg); }
            20% { transform: translate(-3px, 0px) rotate(1deg); }
            30% { transform: translate(3px, 2px) rotate(0deg); }
            40% { transform: translate(1px, -1px) rotate(1deg); }
            50% { transform: translate(-1px, 2px) rotate(-1deg); }
            60% { transform: translate(-3px, 1px) rotate(0deg); }
            70% { transform: translate(3px, 1px) rotate(-1deg); }
            80% { transform: translate(-1px, -1px) rotate(1deg); }
            90% { transform: translate(1px, 2px) rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: translate(1px, -2px) rotate(-1deg); }
        }
        .screen-shake { animation: shake 0.4s; }
        
        @keyframes flash-green { 0% { box-shadow: inset 0 0 50px var(--neon-green); } 100% { box-shadow: none; } }
        .flash-success { animation: flash-green 0.5s; }

        @keyframes flash-red { 0% { box-shadow: inset 0 0 50px var(--neon-red); } 100% { box-shadow: none; } }
        .flash-danger { animation: flash-red 0.5s; }

        /* Scrollbar */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--dark-bg); }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #30363d; border-radius: 4px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: var(--cyber-blue); }

        /* Timer Bar */
        .timer-track { background: #30363d; width: 100%; height: 8px; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; }
        .timer-fill { background: var(--cyber-blue); height: 100%; width: 100%; transition: width 0.1s linear, background-color 0.3s; }
        .timer-warning { background: var(--neon-red); }

        #toast-container { position: fixed; top: 20px; right: 20px; z-index: 100; }
        .toast { background: var(--panel-bg); border: 1px solid var(--neon-green); color: var(--neon-green); padding: 10px 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--neon-green); opacity: 0; transform: translateX(100%); transition: all 0.5s ease; }
        .toast.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center p-4">

    <!-- Toast Notifications -->
    <div id="toast-container"></div>

    <!-- AUDIO CONTROLS -->
    <div class="fixed top-4 right-4 z-50 flex items-center gap-2">
        <button id="btn-mute" class="text-xs font-mono cyber-panel p-2 text-gray-400 hover:text-white" onclick="toggleMute()">
            🔊 BGM: ON
        </button>
    </div>

    <!-- MAIN CONTAINER -->
    <main class="w-full max-w-3xl flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center">
        
        <!-- SECTION 1: GATEWAY & BRIEFING -->
        <section id="sec-gateway" class="cyber-panel p-6 md:p-10 flex flex-col gap-6 animate-fade-in">
            <div class="text-center">
                <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2 neon-text-blue tracking-wider">EMOTIONAL VAULT</h1>
                <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300">Setoran vs Tarikan</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-black/50 p-4 border-l-4 border-cyan-400 rounded">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-cyan-400 text-lg mb-2">💡 WHY WE PLAY (Mission Objective)</h3>
                <p class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-2">
                    Kelancaran operasional cabang tidak hanya bergantung pada SOP, tetapi pada <b>Psychological Safety</b> dan <b>Saldo Relasi</b>. Kebiasaan menyalahkan (Tarikan) akan menutup transparansi, sementara merespons masalah dengan konstruktif (Setoran) akan membangun stabilitas tim.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
                    <b>Misi Anda:</b> Terapkan metode <b>P-A-S (Pause, Assess, Support)</b> untuk memilah secara instan mana perilaku yang mengisi "Bank Emosi" dan mana yang mengurasnya!
                </p>
            </div>

            <form id="form-login" class="flex flex-col gap-4 mt-4" onsubmit="startGame(event)">
                <div class="flex flex-col">
                    <label class="text-sm text-cyan-400 mb-1 font-mono">NAMA LENGKAP</label>
                    <input type="text" id="input-nama" required class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-600 rounded p-2 text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-cyan-400" placeholder="Masukkan nama Anda...">
